body.description: Nuby’s 3-D Sili Soother Pacifiers are ideal for use between feedings. The Sili Soother Pacifiers help calm your little one when they get fussy. With a soothing, comfortable sit, the all-silicone pacifier is designed to be lightweight so your baby will have an easier time keeping it in their mouth, rather than dropping it on the floor. The 3-D Sili Soother Pacifiers come two to a package, so you always have a spare pacifier that your child will love. With its 3-D design, the Sili Soother Pacifiers are sure to bring a smile to you and your little one’s face. Nuby always keeps you and your family’s safety in mind. The 3-D Sili Soother Pacifiers are made of 100% silicone, which is BPA-free and made to last.

productInformation.name: Safety warning
productInformation.value: ‎WARNING: Do Not Tie Pacifier Around Child’s Neck As It Presents A Strangulation Danger. To prevent the possibility of choking, always test strength by pulling on bulb portion of nipple. Regularly inspect pacifier for excessive signs of wear and replace if unit becomes sticky, enlarged, or cracked. Always use this product with adult supervision. IMPORTANT: Remove any plastic attachments and packaging before giving to children.

productInformation.name: Care instructions
productInformation.value: ‎CLEANING: Wash and boil pacifier for up to 2 minutes prior to initial use. Wash regularly with hot, soapy water and rinse well. Dry thoroughly.
